summary: OLAF - Olaf is a new token on the Ethereum blockchain that draws inspiration from the beloved character, Olaf, from the movie Frozen. This token incorporates the playful and whimsical nature of the snowman Olaf, making it an appealing choice for fans of the franchise. One notable feature of Olaf token is its 0% tax, which means that there are no additional fees imposed on transactions. Additionally, liquidity for Olaf token will been burned, which adds to the scarcity and value of the token, especially during the hype surrounding Christmas.
